data.title: 13 Coins in WA
data.meta_description: See the menus for 13 Coins in WA. Offering prime rib dip, steaks, cocktails, wine and more for outdoor seating, kerbside-pickup, no-contact delivery, delivery, takeaway and dine-in!
data.text:
*Please note: Consumption of raw or undercooked meats, poultry, eggs, fish or shellfish may increase your risk of foodborne illness. Raw egg is used in Caesar salad dressing. A Service Charge of 4% will be added to all checks. This is retained by 13 Coins. This is not a gratuity for service staff. An 18% gratuity will be added to parties of 10 or more, of which approximately 70% is retained by your server and 30% is distributed to kitchen and support staff

*Please note: Consumption of raw or undercooked meats, poultry, eggs, fish or shellfish may increase your risk of foodborne illness. Raw egg is used in Caesar salad dressing. Due to initiatives to amend state minimum wage and benefits, a Service Charge of 4% will be added to all checks. This is not a gratuity for service staff. An 18% gratuity will be added to parties of 10 or more, of which 100% is paid to service and kitchen staff

**Consuming raw or undercooked meats, poultry, seafood, shellfish and eggs increase your risk of foodborne illness. *Option for Gluten Free Pasta or Bread 24% Service Charge, $7 Tray Charge plus all applicable taxes applied to each order.
